snippet: Kenyan authorities on Monday charged a Venezuelan diplomat with the murder of Venezuala’s acting ambassador to Kenya.
abstract: Kenyan authorities charge Venezuelan diplomat Dwight Sagaray with the murder of Olga Fonseca Gimenez, Venezuela’s acting ambassador to Kenya, in what police believe was a killing motivated by a battle over leadership of the Venezuelan Embassy.
lead_paragraph: Kenyan authorities on Monday charged a Venezuelan diplomat with the murder of Venezuala’s acting ambassador to Kenya.

headline.main: Kenya: Venezuelan Diplomat Is Charged in Embassy Murder
headline.print_headline: Kenya: Venezuelan Diplomat Is Charged in Embassy Murder
